{"tid":1875282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼醫用級口罩上線啦！","createTime":"2020-02-11T16:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T08:16:45.000Z","uid":232237,"like":25,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"43f245ff14a1adf2e5bc26cdc7f0f431aaca63ee","tid":1875282,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼醫用級口罩預訂<br />\n貨到先pm大家收錢<br />\n<br />\n終於比我地搵到貨源, 希望訂貨返嚟順順利利，此款口罩係印尼醫用，VFE,BFE, PFE &gt; 99.9% ，成本價加運費預計 $60盒(50個)。<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋希望更多人可以買到，所以每人最多可訂2盒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已落單訂貨，不是現貨，預計3月初可到港，請大家真係想買的先好留言，因為想幫到更多嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再三重申，我哋貨到再收錢！<br />\n<br />\n有需要既朋友做以下步驟<br />\n1. 正皮呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 留言註明數量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 去窗口大叫 我想講連尼住含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋會盡力安排，希望為連登仔加油打氣，為有需要嘅人出一分力，但我哋都不敢確定出貨是否順利，如最後運輸不成功，請大家多多見諒!<br />\n<br />\n#絕對成本價發售 <br />\n#貨價加運費幾錢就幾錢賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spYUdx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspYUdx3.jpg&h=494ade60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"850db83c3f020c40a376e8904869decc05af87d1","tid":1875282,"uid":346806,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"假到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n数？"},{"pid":"3de06d805f44cc6ccdc292308f7f4bbe7e30b13a","tid":1875282,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"叫咗！真係有！"},{"pid":"e8bc4cc8b1d46b8bcd7b78053b8ed4cb5bb1f